Package bignumber

Interface BigNumberListNode

public interface BigNumberListNode
This interface represents all operations for a node in a list of BigNumber implemented as an ADT.

      int compare(BigNumberListNode other)
      It compares each node of this BigNumberListNode to the other BigNumberListNode to determine which number is bigger, smaller or equal to.
      Parameters:

      Returns:
